com.phunware.advertising

Interface PwAdRequest.Builder

  • Enclosing interface:
    PwAdRequest

    public static interface PwAdRequest.Builder
    Builder object used to generate customized PwAdRequest objects.

    Example Usage

     PwAdRequest.Builder builder = PwAdvertisingModule.getPwAdRequestBuilder("YOUR_ZONE_ID")
                                          // enable test mode during development
                                          .setTestMode(true)

                                          // allow gps data to be used in ad request
                                          .setLocationTrackingEnabled(true)

                                          // add relevant keywords to improve ad relevance
                                          .setKeywords(listOfKeywords);
 PwAdRequest request = builder.getPwAdRequest();
